messages.text: I can’t live without you. Give me today to prove that we belong together.
you have the same feelings for me.

im here, but where are you?
im sitting in the same corner seat where you first met me
your whole life has been playing it safe
a Medium latte, skim milk, extra shot of espresso should be coming your way

because I pay attention to you
